name: Kongsfjorden monitoring data - grid - 2006
description: In 1997 and 1998 soft-bottom fauna of the arcticglacial fjord Kongsfjorden was extensively sampled and majorcommunities were identified along the fjordaxis, which were believed to be relatedto the diminishing influence of the glacial activity. This setof data was collected as part of a PhD programme and was the result of repeated samplingin search for natural or climate driven communitychanges.
